01:01:11.314 --> 01:01:13.149
You wrote a lot of posts too.

01:01:13.232 --> 01:01:15.401
Your writing skills were superb.
For example…

01:01:18.571 --> 01:01:20.865
"Am I the only one
who thinks Ma Yeong-suk is pretty?"

01:01:20.948 --> 01:01:23.493
"I think she's so pretty too."

01:01:23.576 --> 01:01:26.329
"Yeah, she is so stylish
and sophisticated."

01:01:27.121 --> 01:01:29.373
"Honestly, aside from age, Ma Yeong-suk…"

01:01:29.457 --> 01:01:31.417
-"is better than Elijah."
-She must be crazy.

01:01:36.631 --> 01:01:37.757
They're all fabricated.

01:01:37.840 --> 01:01:39.091
She did that all by herself?

01:01:39.175 --> 01:01:41.385
-Has she nothing else to do?
-That is so embarrassing.

01:01:41.469 --> 01:01:43.387
-Seriously.
-That's so…

01:01:43.471 --> 01:01:44.764
What an intense life you have.

01:01:48.226 --> 01:01:52.355
Your Honor, when people see
celebrities like Elijah,

01:01:52.438 --> 01:01:54.357
they scream their names and envy them.

01:01:54.440 --> 01:01:57.235
But they're actually lonelier
and weaker than anyone else.

01:01:59.195 --> 01:02:01.739
Even as they bleed
from the dagger-like words of people

01:02:01.823 --> 01:02:03.366
who speak recklessly about others,

01:02:03.449 --> 01:02:06.327
it's not easy for them
to say that it hurts.

01:02:08.162 --> 01:02:09.413
Think about it.

01:02:10.248 --> 01:02:13.543
How many times have we lost

01:02:14.836 --> 01:02:16.712
those lonely and vulnerable stars

01:02:18.798 --> 01:02:20.424
that shined…

01:02:22.593 --> 01:02:24.554
so brightly?

01:02:28.391 --> 01:02:32.144
Does the price for popularity
have to be that cruel?

01:02:40.111 --> 01:02:40.945
Ms. Ma.

01:02:42.572 --> 01:02:44.407
You must take responsibility now

01:02:44.490 --> 01:02:47.493
for that persistent spite
and obsession of yours.

01:02:49.704 --> 01:02:51.831
What did I do that was so wrong?

01:02:52.456 --> 01:02:53.416
What?

01:02:53.499 --> 01:02:56.127
I only fought
for the public's right to know!

01:02:56.210 --> 01:02:58.713
At least, I don't hide in the shadows
like a coward!

01:03:00.756 --> 01:03:04.427
My client is not a coward
who hides in the shadows.

01:03:06.804 --> 01:03:08.222
Please come in.

01:03:13.311 --> 01:03:14.186
Oh, my gosh!

01:03:14.270 --> 01:03:15.187
-It's Elijah!
-Elijah!

01:03:18.274 --> 01:03:19.692
Order in the court!

01:03:19.775 --> 01:03:22.486
-Bailiff.
-Order in the court!

01:03:23.738 --> 01:03:25.907
Is the plaintiff
attending the trial in person?

01:03:29.201 --> 01:03:31.829
Yes, Your Honor.
My apologies for being late.

01:03:37.501 --> 01:03:40.671
Your Honor, the plaintiff would like
to share something.

01:03:40.755 --> 01:03:43.299
May she have a chance to speak?

01:03:43.925 --> 01:03:45.176
You may proceed.

01:03:56.312 --> 01:04:00.358
First off, I apologize to everyone
who was disappointed in me

01:04:00.441 --> 01:04:01.442
because of this incident.

01:04:09.033 --> 01:04:10.576
No matter what the reason was,

01:04:10.660 --> 01:04:13.913
it was my fault for cursing
and throwing stuff

01:04:14.747 --> 01:04:16.040
at the young students.

01:04:16.123 --> 01:04:18.542
I will compensate them for all damages

01:04:18.626 --> 01:04:19.835
and apologize to them.

01:04:20.628 --> 01:04:23.631
I will become a more mature person
so that I won't let down

01:04:24.548 --> 01:04:26.342
those who support and love me.

01:04:34.433 --> 01:04:35.476
But here…

01:04:41.315 --> 01:04:43.067
I'll call her the defendant.

01:04:43.150 --> 01:04:46.195
I have something to say to the defendant.

01:04:46.278 --> 01:04:47.113
Okay.

01:04:51.993 --> 01:04:53.327
I am standing

01:04:54.370 --> 01:04:55.663
right in front of you.

01:04:56.789 --> 01:04:58.499
Look me in the eyes,

01:05:00.292 --> 01:05:01.502
and do it.

01:05:02.044 --> 01:05:02.878
Do what?

01:05:03.879 --> 01:05:05.715
All those things

01:05:05.798 --> 01:05:07.800
you have said about me.

01:05:09.969 --> 01:05:11.387
The lies.

01:05:14.223 --> 01:05:15.641
Those filthy words.

01:05:15.725 --> 01:05:19.812
Those words didn't hurt just me.

01:05:22.648 --> 01:05:24.275
They hurt my fans,

01:05:25.860 --> 01:05:27.528
who I love more than anyone else.

01:05:34.410 --> 01:05:37.997
Elijah! I'm a fan
who supports you from Japan.

01:05:38.080 --> 01:05:42.293
I'm working on my own dreams
as I listen to your music.

01:05:42.376 --> 01:05:45.337
So, please stay strong!

01:05:45.421 --> 01:05:49.550
There are many more fans who love you,
so don't worry and trust in us.

01:05:49.633 --> 01:05:52.178
Elijah, I love you. Stay strong.

01:05:52.261 --> 01:05:54.764
I'll protect you. Good luck.

01:05:54.847 --> 01:05:58.225
When I was at my lowest,
your songs cheered me up.

01:05:58.309 --> 01:05:59.602
-I love Elijah.
-I love you.

01:05:59.685 --> 01:06:01.437
-Let's go!
-Stay strong!

01:06:02.146 --> 01:06:05.024
-We'll protect you, Elijah!
-Ponies are always by your side!

01:06:05.107 --> 01:06:06.150
Hang in there!

01:06:06.233 --> 01:06:09.070
We love you, Elijah!

01:06:09.153 --> 01:06:10.362
Go, Elijah!

01:06:10.446 --> 01:06:12.031
-Elijah, let's go!
-We love you!

01:06:12.114 --> 01:06:14.492
-Hang in there!
-We love you! Stay strong!

01:06:22.249 --> 01:06:25.711
Okay, then. Say it to my face now.

01:06:29.548 --> 01:06:31.425
Those awful words that hurt

01:06:31.509 --> 01:06:33.511
the ones who love my music quietly

01:06:34.970 --> 01:06:37.765
and the ones who trust and love me.

01:06:37.848 --> 01:06:40.976
Look me in the eyes and say them

01:06:43.145 --> 01:06:47.316
instead of cowardly hiding
behind the mask you call "the public."

01:06:56.700 --> 01:06:58.244
Gosh, Elijah is so tough.

01:06:59.245 --> 01:07:02.540
This is why I can't stop loving her.

01:07:05.709 --> 01:07:07.211
Your eyes are boring through her.

01:07:23.519 --> 01:07:27.273
EASTERN DISTRICT COURT

01:07:27.356 --> 01:07:28.190
Judge Kang.

01:07:30.192 --> 01:07:32.820
I mean, Attorney Kang.

01:07:32.903 --> 01:07:33.779
What is it?

01:07:35.656 --> 01:07:37.616
Are you really going to
see this to the end?

01:07:37.700 --> 01:07:40.244
We'll stop now
if you pay the 100 million at once.

01:07:41.036 --> 01:07:42.371
Let's stop here.

01:07:42.454 --> 01:07:44.999
It won't benefit either side to continue.

01:07:45.833 --> 01:07:46.792
I don't think so.

01:07:46.876 --> 01:07:48.544
We'll have many benefits.

01:07:50.546 --> 01:07:51.714
We were thinking

01:07:51.797 --> 01:07:56.010
of taking all the cases from every star
who's been harassed by the defendant.

01:07:59.597 --> 01:08:00.681
Do you know

01:08:00.764 --> 01:08:03.934
who informed us about Elijah's boyfriend?

01:08:06.061 --> 01:08:06.896
Do you?

01:08:07.688 --> 01:08:11.442
Who is this person
that you're taking so long to reveal?

01:08:15.779 --> 01:08:16.614
There she comes.

01:08:17.990 --> 01:08:18.824
It's her.

01:08:21.952 --> 01:08:23.037
Ms. Cha Jin-hui.

01:08:23.913 --> 01:08:25.331
Pick whichever one you need.

01:08:26.749 --> 01:08:27.958
Elijah!

01:08:28.542 --> 01:08:30.920
My goodness, congratulations!

01:08:33.088 --> 01:08:36.842
-Congratulations!
-Elijah's mother tipped us off herself.

01:08:37.760 --> 01:08:38.761
Do you know that?

01:08:39.762 --> 01:08:44.058
I had been so angry
because of Ma Yeong-suk.

01:08:45.809 --> 01:08:46.936
How did you make time?

01:08:47.937 --> 01:08:49.730
Well, I just had to come, of course.

01:08:56.362 --> 01:08:58.155
STAY TUNED TO WATCH THE EPILOGUE

01:09:16.257 --> 01:09:17.341
But they're family.

01:09:17.424 --> 01:09:19.134
How could a parent
do that to her child?

01:09:19.218 --> 01:09:21.262
Drive those losers away, okay?

01:09:21.345 --> 01:09:22.972
Elijah, what brings you here?

01:09:23.055 --> 01:09:25.140
I want to end the exclusive contract
with my company.

01:09:25.224 --> 01:09:26.225
Please file a lawsuit.

01:09:26.308 --> 01:09:27.851
What have I done that was so wrong?

01:09:27.935 --> 01:09:30.437
I've only done my best for my daughter.

01:09:30.521 --> 01:09:32.815
We tracked it down,
and it was a life insurance plan.

01:09:32.898 --> 01:09:34.191
A life insurance for Elijah.

01:09:34.275 --> 01:09:36.485
Wasn't the failed investment
due to accounting fraud?

01:09:36.568 --> 01:09:38.445
No! Those were all fabricated!

01:09:38.529 --> 01:09:39.947
Exemption of Crimes by Family.

01:09:40.030 --> 01:09:43.575
Property crimes committed
within family cannot be punished.

01:09:43.659 --> 01:09:45.160
Just please sue me.

01:09:45.244 --> 01:09:47.288
Elijah. Is this what you wanted?

01:09:47.371 --> 01:09:49.164
Stop that lawsuit at once.

01:09:49.248 --> 01:09:50.207
And break up the team.

01:09:50.291 --> 01:09:53.168
Mr. Kang. We have to do something.

01:09:53.252 --> 01:09:54.378
Let's go.

01:09:54.461 --> 01:09:55.921
The biggest stage would be…

01:09:56.005 --> 01:09:57.506
Let's go to the National Assembly.

01:10:00.592 --> 01:10:01.677
Mr. Kang…

01:10:03.554 --> 01:10:04.847
Park Gi-ppeum.

01:10:07.057 --> 01:10:08.851
How can you do this to me?

01:10:11.186 --> 01:10:13.439
Of all people,
you should've trusted me.

01:10:15.858 --> 01:10:17.401
You didn't trust me,

01:10:18.068 --> 01:10:19.194
so it made me upset.

01:10:23.699 --> 01:10:24.575
I'm sad.

01:10:26.577 --> 01:10:27.703
Oh, my gosh!

01:10:27.786 --> 01:10:29.330
-Nurse! He's…
-Yes.

01:10:29.413 --> 01:10:31.290
The anesthesia hasn't worn off yet.

01:10:33.250 --> 01:10:34.126
Is that so?

01:10:36.920 --> 01:10:38.380
I'm so upset.

01:10:38.464 --> 01:10:39.882
I'm hurt.

01:10:40.758 --> 01:10:42.843
I'm so hurt.

01:10:44.386 --> 01:10:46.013
You hurt my feelings.

01:10:47.514 --> 01:10:48.557
I feel so sad.

